      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Every time I'm in a waiting room I feel the urge to write.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And this week, I sat in two.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Marketers talk an awful lot about how to get how get customers in the proverbial door. And organizations spend a ton heeding their advice.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Yet many organizations fall short when the prospect has ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "arrived",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": ".",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Waiting, perhaps patiently, for their turn to partake in the service they're offering.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "I wonder why most don't think that finding ways to expedite that process (or capitalize on it) is time or money well spent.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If it gets them in door ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "and keeps them coming back",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " it's usually worth making it a priority.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}